{
  "stem": "9725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And perhaps I should mention that my father's family, who lived on the border of Romania and Russia, was very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to visit there until my grandmother moved away from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was probably eight or nine, maybe 10.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to visit there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was, in my memory, it remains like a portrait of Chagall, you know-- the market, and the horses, and the enormous sunflowers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would say that, emotionally, I feel much closer to my father's family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think some of the legacy of the stories which my father talked about-- his father, who was an orthodox Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know if this is the time to tell you the story about him-- I think it deeply-- has influenced me, and I think that my own religious beliefs, and whatever spiritual substance I got-- I got from my father's family.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even so, you know, my mother's family was much more modern, and what was it-- I-- I do think that-- that there was a much deeper, much more spiritual thing in my father's family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I still feel quite tied to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always wanted to write.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always wanted to have all of my stories to have happy endings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the orphans found their parents on some desert islands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always wanted to be pretty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always wanted to be-- where my brother was very good looking, my mother was a renowned beauty, and I was always sort of a bit in the shadows.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I-- I tried to-- to overcompensate it in-- in a little, different ways.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very shy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Painfully shy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I loved animals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was always a lot of animals that I cared for, particularly cats.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
